      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s full of heart! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear that tells the story of its reliable service. It\u2019s a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for a practical ride that still has plenty of miles left to offer. If you're looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done with a smile, this is the one for you!",
