    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable, functional option for daily transportation. The exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable surface scratches, a few small door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but displays some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat and high-touch surfaces. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it may require more frequent routine maintenance compared to a newer model. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly, honest vehicle.",
