      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of peerless quality. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, having been preserved with an exacting attention to detail that satisfies the most discerning collector. Both the mechanical systems and the aesthetic finish are impeccable, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is rarely encountered in the secondary market. This is a definitive opportunity to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade caliber.",
